{
  "chapter": 7,
  "chapter_summary": "第七回　英雄之会：本章围绕主要人物的遭遇、江湖见闻与冲突推进展开。第七回英雄之会片刻，叶老二就回来了，带着熊倜走到里面，穿过走廊，便到了那间书房。叶老二到了书房后说道：\"你我自己弟兄，也不要再客气了，需要什么，等会儿我叫一个小童站在门口，你就对他说好了，熊兄此刻看看夏女侠的伤势，然后再到前面来谈谈。熊倜检查了夏芸的伤势，用内力把她伤势止住，然后走出房外。他走到前房，看见叶家兄弟以及马氏兄弟、尚未明等人章节中人物往来、言语试探和武林局势互相交织，为后续恩怨、师承与行动埋下线索。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_wei_ming",
      "speaker_name": "尚未明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "说起来，我的身世比大哥更惨。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "叶老大",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "莫等闲，白了少年头，空悲切。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_yun",
      "speaker_name": "夏芸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快去睡吧，你瞧你这样子，我看着都生气。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "畜生，谁是你的师父。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "弟子不敢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么敢不敢的，你连我的话都敢不听吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我的话你听见没有？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "弟子听见了！只是……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没有什么只是不只是的，快站起来和我动手。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我偶游太行，却无意中听得天阴教主焦异行，从手下处得到柄名剑，剑名",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你怎么找到他的呀？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "头子",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "带他进来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小李，将那双鞋子拿过来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "穿上。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当家的想必是误会了，有话慢慢地说，我……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "倚天剑",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么我到底和你有什么深仇大怨，你非要杀我不可？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这老介福鞋店可是在当涂城里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "该，该，熊大侠怎么说怎么办好了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这倒真谢谢了。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既是这样，我就收下了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "下次我再也不喝那么多酒了，现在还有点酒气呢。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 496,
      "line_end": 496
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怎么，她不在屋里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 510
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "叶老大",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怎么，她没有和你在一起？屋里没人呀！",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 512,
      "line_end": 512
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "少说大话。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 598,
      "line_end": 598
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还有熊倜。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 658,
      "line_end": 658
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只要捉了夏芸，熊倜还怕不来找她吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 660,
      "line_end": 660
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这粉蝶果然心思灵敏。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 662,
      "line_end": 662
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "叶老大",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这件事在我兄弟处发生，我兄弟也要算上一个。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 678,
      "line_end": 678
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_wei_ming",
      "speaker_name": "尚未明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怎么样，我说有船吧！",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 714,
      "line_end": 714
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_wei_ming",
      "speaker_name": "尚未明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可不可以找那位相公商量一下，船钱我们出好了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 726,
      "line_end": 726
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不客气又怎么样？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 736,
      "line_end": 736
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大哥，你认识他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 756,
      "line_end": 756
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_hao",
      "speaker_name": "边浩",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "阁下何人？为何发笑？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 774,
      "line_end": 774
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_wei_ming",
      "speaker_name": "尚未明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我笑你的剑今日只怕真要过瘾了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 776,
      "line_end": 776
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_hao",
      "speaker_name": "边浩",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你是什么东西，也配向我叫阵？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 778,
      "line_end": 778
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_wei_ming",
      "speaker_name": "尚未明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我正要问你是什么东西，也配向我大哥叫阵？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 780,
      "line_end": 780
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "贤弟不要包揽，这人是我的，不管你的事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 786,
      "line_end": 786
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_wei_ming",
      "speaker_name": "尚未明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只怕今日是谁教训谁还不一定呢！",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 792,
      "line_end": 792
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_hao",
      "speaker_name": "边浩",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我先教训教训你。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 794,
      "line_end": 794
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你两人都不能动手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 804,
      "line_end": 804
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_wei_ming",
      "speaker_name": "尚未明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 806,
      "line_end": 806
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_wei_ming",
      "speaker_name": "尚未明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你认得此人吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 808,
      "line_end": 808
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_hao",
      "speaker_name": "边浩",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你又知道他是什么人吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 812,
      "line_end": 812
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就好了，你两人既然互不相识，怎能随便动手？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 816,
      "line_end": 816
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_hao",
      "speaker_name": "边浩",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你也知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 828,
      "line_end": 828
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_wei_ming",
      "speaker_name": "尚未明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当然，当然。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 830,
      "line_end": 830
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_wei_ming",
      "speaker_name": "尚未明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "岂敢，岂敢，正是区区在下。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 838,
      "line_end": 838
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "确实该打。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 894,
      "line_end": 894
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "先打他的屁股。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 914,
      "line_end": 914
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "晚辈不敢，请问两位老前辈的尊号？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 974,
      "line_end": 974
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "晚辈熊倜，这一个是晚辈的盟弟尚未明。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 980,
      "line_end": 980
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "尚未明，这个名字倒真有意思。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 982,
      "line_end": 982
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "喂，你说尚未明这名字有没有意思？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 984,
      "line_end": 984
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "熊倜、熊倜……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 986,
      "line_end": 986
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_wei_ming",
      "speaker_name": "尚未明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "多谢老前辈。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 996,
      "line_end": 996
    }
  ],
